data.description: Welcome to the Heart of Chicago - this is a fully renovated legal 3-flat with an adjacent lot, 2143 W Coulter + 2 Car Garage. Two property pins.  Plans and Permits were obtained, and the building underwent a complete interior transformation in 2023 including new electricity, new plumbing, new HVAC systems, brand new layout, windows, foundation, and a brand-new enclosed porch. Modern interiors feature beautiful brand-new hardwood floors, quartz countertops, ann sacks backsplash tile, and high ceilings. Each kitchen includes a stove, a fridge, a microwave, a dishwasher, a hood range, and quartz countertops, with beautiful backsplash. Washer/Dryer in each unit. All appliances were purchased new in 2023. New enclosed porch. Cherry Tree on the adjacent lot. Conveniently located near the Pink Line, buses, and downtown. Steps away from the proposed Paseo Trail.
